{"tid":1496764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰壓迫員工係被逼，大家唔好鬧國泰，林奠都係被逼，如果國泰領頭大罷工，結果會點？","createTime":"2019-08-22T16:07:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T01:19:16.000Z","uid":152084,"like":28,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7c0defe27ef0bbe060c7c6cb81208e02d6fd416e","tid":1496764,"uid":152084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:07:22.000Z","msg":"國泰係被逼，雖然佢散播白色恐佈，但係放過佢啦，<span style=\"color: red;\">好人CEO都走左</span>，放過佢啦。<br />\n<br />\n林奠係被逼，放過佢啦。<br />\n<br />\n全港出聲既商戶都係被逼，放過佢啦。<br />\n<br />\n國泰呢單嘢如果唔反擊，等睇下個月全港商戶跪低，然後全部連登仔放過佢地。中共咁明顯搞國泰就係要你班航空職員跪低，因為機場運作就係中共個春袋。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">知唔知國泰領頭大罷工，結果會點？<br />\n1.國泰再次跪低，不過係跪向香港人<br />\n2.中共唔俾跪，達成攬炒大計</span></span><br />\n<br />\n日日塞機場可以搞到幾時？而家呢個咁好既時間，國泰全體員工反擊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c34138a4001d3f477ce073d26f731948fdf92e8","tid":1496764,"uid":152084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:09:08.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"fc380908830412d039c61a7c525f1fd8b1fa566a","tid":1496764,"uid":152084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:09:21.000Z","msg":"x2"},{"pid":"27181c9612c8962a02cb7b565e81c163f50e7d70","tid":1496764,"uid":152084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:09:56.000Z","msg":"x3"},{"pid":"2e28a82823d183b90f1e77ffb16677f1f0a6ac75","tid":1496764,"uid":152084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:10:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1e68ffee71b7098bcd5da0a05347cb78d8c251","tid":1496764,"uid":31151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:11:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>咁都忍得 屎都食得 立即罷工 刻不容緩</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"6e0d6299a88829b34459